But it's pretty big.

14
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:11,620
我会拿下它的
I'm gonna win it.

15
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:14,720
我觉得你肯定会赢得它的
It wouldn't surprise me a bit if you did.

16
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:17,490
金牌颁给有圣奥尔登价值观的人
It's given to the person who exemplifies St. Alden's values.

17
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:20,090
