00:49:34,600 --> 00:49:41,340
我理解你对麦洛的悲痛
I understand that your friend Milo recently passed away.

787
00:49:41,440 --> 00:49:44,110
说得没错
That's right.

788
00:49:44,180 --> 00:49:46,180
你对这件事的感受如何
How did that make you feel?

789
00:49:50,020 --> 00:49:52,680
我肯定你很难受吧
Pretty sad, I bet.

790
00:49:52,750 --> 00:49:56,390
我哭了两天
I cried for two days.

791
00:49:56,490 --> 00:49:58,520
哦
Oh.

792
00:49:58,590 --> 00:50:01,730
我理解你
I understand.

793
00:50:01,790 --> 00:50:06,030
这是你第一次看到认识的人去世吗
Was that the first time someone you knew died?

794
00:50:09,000 --> 00:50:10,570
不是
No.

795
00:50:16,280 --> 00:50:17,710
哦
Oh.

796
00:50:17,810 --> 00:50:20,040
明白了
I see.

797
00:50:20,150 --> 00:50:22,750
马奇医生
Dr. March?

798
00:50:22,820 --> 00:50:25,820
为什么人去世时 他身边的人会伤心呢
Why do people get so upset when people die?

799
00:50:25,890 --> 00:50:29,150
这事迟早会发生在每个人身上啊
It's gonna happen to everyone sooner or later.

800
00:50:29,220 --> 00:50:31,460
问得好 艾玛
It's a great question, Emma.

801
00:50:31,520 --> 00:50:36,090
我们知道这事不可逆 但依旧会很痛心
We all do know it's inevitable and we grieve anyway.

802
00:50:36,200 --> 00:50:40,830
为他而感到同情
To feel or to have empathy for others

803
00:50:40,830 --> 00:50:43,730
这是我们人的本性
is what it means to be human.

804
00:50:56,580 --> 00:50:59,450
艾玛 我要告诉你个秘密
Emma, I'm going to tell you a secret.

805
00:50:59,520 --> 00:51:03,450
我像你那么大的时候我也这么做过
I did the exact same things as you when I was your age.

806
00:51:09,330 --> 00:51:11,060
你们俩看起来挺融洽嘛
Well, you two seemed to really hit it off.

807
00:51:11,130 --> 00:51:13,600
我们谈的很畅快 是吧 艾玛
Oh, we had a great talk, didn't we, Emma?

808
00:51:13,700 --> 00:51:15,070
当然
Yes.

809
00:51:15,170 --> 00:51:16,470
爸爸 我能出去玩会吗
Daddy, can I go outside?

810
00:51:16,570 --> 00:51:17,740
当然
Sure.

811
00:51:19,140 --> 00:51:21,870
格罗斯曼先生 我在职业生涯里见过
Mr. Grossman, I have seen thousands of kids

812
00:51:21,970 --> 00:51:23,510
许多孩子
in my practise,

813
00:51:23,610 --> 00:51:27,750
艾玛是我遇到的最正常的孩子
and Emma seems 100 percent perfectly average.

814
00:51:29,080 --> 00:51:33,820
实际上 和她聊天让我想起了小时候
In fact, I told her she reminds me of myself.

815
00:52:06,520 --> 00:52:07,850
你好
Hey there.

816
00:52:07,920 --> 00:52:09,050
嘿
Hey.

817
00:52:09,120 --> 00:52:11,390
检查得怎么样
How'd the appointment go?

818
00:52:11,460 --> 00:52:12,420
很好
Fine.

819
00:52:15,700 --> 00:52:17,800
艾玛在楼上
Emma's up in her room.

820
00:52:17,860 --> 00:52:21,100
那么 我得穿上衣服
Well, I guess I better put on some clothes,

821
00:52:21,200 --> 00:52:22,870
上去看看了
head up there.

822
00:52:22,940 --> 00:52:25,540
希望你不会介意我趁机晒晒太阳
I hope you don't mind me taking advantage of the sun.

823
00:52:25,610 --> 00:52:28,970
不 你得抓紧时间好好享受
No, you... gotta take advantage of it.

824
00:52:31,610 --> 00:52:33,180
确实得抓紧时间
Gotta take advantage.

825
00:52:33,280 --> 00:52:34,810
没错
Yep.

826
00:52:45,290 --> 00:52:47,630
你没有朋友吗
Don't you have any friends?

827
00:52:47,730 --> 00:52:49,760
关你什么事
What do you care?

828
00:52:49,830 --> 00:52:51,700
显然大家都认为你有精神病
Clearly everyone thinks you're mental.

829
00:52:51,760 --> 00:52:53,160
随你怎么说
Whatever, Chloe.

830
00:52:53,230 --> 00:52:54,670
现在大家都知道
Now that everyone knows

831
00:52:54,730 --> 00:52:58,170
你偷了那孩子的奖牌 只是时间问题
you stole that dead kid's medal it's just a matter of time.

832
00:52:58,270 --> 00:53:00,270
什么时间问题
A matter of time until what?

833
00:53:00,340 --> 00:53:02,110
调查出你对他做了什么
They find out what you did to him.

834
00:53:02,210 --> 00:53:04,310
我听不懂你在说什么
I don't know what you're talking about.

835
00:53:04,380 --> 00:53:06,380
也许你马上就会被送上电椅了
Maybe you'll end up in the little pink chair.

836
00:53:09,420 --> 00:53:11,150
我马上让爸爸赶走你
I'm gonna have my dad get rid of you.

837
00:53:11,250 --> 00:53:12,250
去啊
Go for it.

838
00:53:12,320 --> 00:53:13,550
他可不会听你的
He won't do it.

839
00:53:13,620 --> 00:53:18,760
你爸爸看上我了
Your dad and I understand each other.

840
00:53:18,860 --> 00:53:20,390
随便你怎么像疯子一样盯着我
You can give me that psycho stare all you want

841
00:53:20,460 --> 00:53:22,830
但告诉你个事实 你爸是个痴男
but the fact is this: your dad's a DILF.

842
00:53:22,930 --> 00:53:25,760
我要定他了 懂吗
D-I-L-F, ok?

843
00:53:25,830 --> 00:53:29,130
他还是单身 他刚才还在打量我身材呢
And he's single, and he was totally just scoping me out.

844
00:53:29,200 --> 00:53:32,270
他和我搞在一起 你不介意吧
You wouldn't mind if he and I hooked up, would you?

845
00:53:32,340 --> 00:53:33,970
可怜的小家伙 放松点
The poor guy needs a release.

846
00:53:34,070 --> 00:53:36,410
我是说 他真不错
I mean, just look at him.

847
00:53:36,510 --> 00:53:39,380
离我爸爸远点
Stay away from my dad.

848
00:53:41,850 --> 00:53:44,750
不然呢
Or what?

849
00:53:44,850 --> 00:53:47,120
我不能做你的继母吗
Wouldn't I make a good stepmom?

850
00:53:49,260 --> 00:53:51,460
你吓不到我的 小不点
You don't scare me, little girl.

851
00:53:51,520 --> 00:53:53,290
我不管 你就只是站在一边
I don't care if you stood there

852
00:53:53,390 --> 00:53:55,590
看着那小孩子淹死
and watched that little kid drown,

853
00:53:55,700 --> 00:53:57,360
还是你把他推下去的
or even if you pushed him in.

854
00:53:57,430 --> 00:54:00,300
在我那 就你这种宠坏的小贱种
Where I come from a spoiled little princess like you

855
00:54:00,400 --> 00:54:04,740
就算是个屁 相信我
ain't nothing, believe me.

856
00:54:04,800 --> 00:54:06,840
威胁别人可不好
It's not nice to threaten people.

857
00:54:06,910 --> 00:54:08,610
但我在你眼里
But you and me?

858
00:54:08,710 --> 00:54:13,410
也不算什么好人 对吧
We're not nice, are we?

859
00:54:35,800 --> 00:54:37,430
噢 艾玛 你吓到我了
Oh, Emma, you scared me.

860
00:54:37,540 --> 00:54:39,740
你喜欢克洛伊吗
Do you like Chloe?

861
00:54:39,840 --> 00:54:40,600
等等 什么
Wait, what?

862
00:54:40,670 --> 00:54:42,510
她说你喜欢她
She said that you like her.

863
00:54:42,580 --> 00:54:47,180
说你 看上她了
That you... understand each other.

864
00:54:47,250 --> 00:54:49,410
她还说她想做我的继母
She said she could be my stepmother some day.

865
00:54:49,520 --> 00:54:50,450
哇 哇 哇
Woah, woah, woah.

866
00:54:50,550 --> 00:54:51,620
等等 让我缓缓
Wait, hold on a second.

867
00:54:51,720 --> 00:54:54,120
首先 这件事绝不可能
First of all, that would never happen,

868
00:54:54,220 --> 00:54:55,920
其次 她为什么要这么说
and why would she say something like that?

869
00:54:56,020 --> 00:54:56,920
你自己清楚
You tell me.

870
00:54:57,020 --> 00:54:58,260
艾玛
Emma.

871
00:54:59,890 --> 00:55:01,890
我不想要继母
I don't want a stepmother.

872
00:55:01,990 --> 00:55:03,360
绝不想
Ever.

873
00:55:07,230 --> 00:55:09,100
没你想象的那么严重
Everything's gonna be ok.

874
00:55:09,170 --> 00:55:12,300
我有约会 不过很快会回来的
I have a meeting but I'll be home early, ok?

875
00:55:12,370 --> 00:55:14,140
回来再说
Then we'll talk.

876
00:55:14,240 --> 00:55:17,840
好吧 我等你回来
Great. I'll wait up.

877
00:55:17,940 --> 00:55:20,110
约会愉快
Have fun on your date!

878
00:55:20,210 --> 00:55:21,350
所以你没再结过婚
So you never remarried?

879
00:55:21,400 --> 00:55:21,800
没有
Nope.

880
00:55:22,000 --> 00:55:24,380
你有多喜欢玩转情场
You like playing the field that much, huh?

881
00:55:24,480 --> 00:55:25,980
简直爱死了
Yeah, I love it.

882
00:55:26,090 --> 00:55:27,890
很让人满足
It's so fulfilling.

883
00:55:27,950 --> 00:55:30,950
你知道吧 特别是抚养一个小女孩
I mean, you know, especially raising a young girl.

884
00:55:38,830 --> 00:55:40,260
很棒
Great.

885
00:55:45,870 --> 00:55:49,370
我开第一家店时折腾了将近四个月
When I first opened the store I had about four months.

886
00:55:49,440 --> 00:55:52,710
我担心店会倒闭 但生意逐渐好了起来
I was really worried but then business picked up

887
00:55:52,780 --> 00:55:55,180
到现在有六年了 都很顺利
and it's been really good for six years now.

888
00:55:55,280 --> 00:55:56,880
艾玛
Emma?

889
00:56:18,200 --> 00:56:20,400
该死的 艾玛
Dammit, Emma.

890
00:56:30,420 --> 00:56:32,120
艾玛
Emma?

891
00:57:00,210 --> 00:57:02,350
艾玛
Emma!

892
00:57:02,420 --> 00:57:05,550
艾玛 快开门 这可不好玩
Emma, let me out of here. This isn't funny.

893
00:57:05,650 --> 00:57:07,020
艾玛
Emma!

894
00:57:33,980 --> 00:57:35,310
艾玛
Emma?

895
00:57:37,980 --> 00:57:39,580
艾玛
Emma!

896
00:57:58,370 --> 00:58:00,340
借过一下 这是我的房子
Let me through! This is my house!

897
00:58:06,250 --> 00:58:07,180
艾玛
Emma!

898
00:58:09,850 --> 00:58:10,050
你是房主吗
Are you the homeowner

899
00:58:10,050 --> 00:58:10,750
是的
Yes.

900
00:58:10,820 --> 00:58:11,050
你是房主吗
Are you the homeowner

901
00:58:11,050 --> 00:58:11,550
没错
Yes, yes.

902
00:58:11,550 --> 00:58:12,820
我有个九岁的女儿 她叫艾玛
I have a nine-year-old daughter, her name is Emma,

903
00:58:12,890 --> 00:58:13,750
她和她保姆一起
she's here with her nanny.

904
00:58:13,850 --> 00:58:14,850
先生 你女儿没事
Sir, your daughter is fine,

905
00:58:14,950 --> 00:58:16,920
她和我们副警长在房子里
she's in a house with one of my deputies.

906
00:58:16,990 --> 00:58:19,220
很不幸 发生了这么突然的事
Now, unfortunately there's been a terrible accident.

907
00:58:19,330 --> 00:58:20,560
那个叫克洛伊的保姆
The nanny, Chloe,

908
00:58:20,630 --> 00:58:22,930
当时还在起火的工棚里
was in the work shed when the fire broke out.

909
00:58:29,340 --> 00:58:30,670
她可能被吓到了
I think she's in shock.

910
00:58:30,740 --> 00:58:32,540
她没告诉我们太多 但他说那个保姆
She hasn't told us much but apparently the young woman

911
00:58:32,610 --> 00:58:36,170
在工棚里偷偷抽烟
would sneak a smoke in the work shed.

912
00:58:44,850 --> 00:58:46,980
好了 给你们一点独处时间
Ok, I will give you two a moment.

913
00:58:53,730 --> 00:58:55,260
小甜熊
Honey bear.

914
00:58:59,270 --> 00:59:01,300
没事了 爸爸
It's ok, daddy.

915
00:59:01,400 --> 00:59:03,700
我没事
Nothing happened to me.

916
00:59:18,720 --> 00:59:20,650
艾玛 我知道你醒着
Emma, I know you're awake.

917
00:59:35,000 --> 00:59:37,070
我觉得我们有麻烦了
I think we're in trouble.

918
00:59:39,970 --> 00:59:43,670
我觉得我们惹上大麻烦了
I think we're both in very big trouble,

919
00:59:43,740 --> 00:59:47,380
我们谈谈 你必须告诉我事情的真相
and we need to talk and I need you to tell me the truth.

920
00:59:51,350 --> 00:59:53,220
我是你父亲 我爱你
I'm your father, I love you,

921
00:59:53,290 --> 00:59:56,220
我会竭尽所能来帮你
I'm going to do anything I can to help you.

922
01:00:05,800 --> 01:00:08,070
是你杀了麦洛 对吧
You hurt Milo, didn't you?

923
01:00:14,110 --> 01:00:15,970
是不是
Didn't you?

924
01:00:17,910 --> 01:00:21,140
他要告状说我拿走了他的奖牌
He was gonna tell on me that I took his medal.

925
01:00:24,020 --> 01:00:27,820
我不想伤害他的
I didn't mean to hurt him.

926
01:00:27,920 --> 01:00:34,660
我推了一下 他就摔下去了
When I pushed him, he fell.

927
01:00:34,730 --> 01:00:39,960
他一直喊 喊着说他不会游泳
He kept on yelling, yelling that he couldn't swim,

928
01:00:40,070 --> 01:00:42,570
但我没有相信他
but I didn't believe him.

929
01:00:42,640 --> 01:00:46,600
他老是夸大事实
He always over-exaggerated.

930
01:00:46,670 --> 01:00:54,440
一会他就没有再喊 然后我再也没看到他了
After a while he stopped yelling and I couldn't see him anymore.

931
01:00:54,510 --> 01:00:57,010
对不起 爸爸
I'm so sorry, daddy.

932
01:00:57,080 --> 01:00:59,750
我不想惹麻烦
I didn't want to get into trouble.

933
01:00:59,850 --> 01:01:01,920
我不会再犯了
I won't do it again.

934
01:01:09,260 --> 01:01:12,630
莱薇娅 片头部分提起过
还有莱薇娅 你的第一任保姆
And Mrs. Levia, your first nanny,

935
01:01:12,700 --> 01:01:15,700
你又把她怎么了
what happed to her?

936
01:01:15,770 --> 01:01:20,240
她紧紧抓着我的手
She should have never grabbed my arm,

937
01:01:20,310 --> 01:01:27,380
所以我踢了她 她就摔下了楼梯
so I kicked her, and she fell down the stairs.

938
01:01:27,480 --> 01:01:29,950
我并没做错什么
I didn't do anything wrong.

939
01:01:30,050 --> 01:01:31,980
她是成年人
She's the adult.

940
01:01:32,050 --> 01:01:36,250
她应该更好地保护自己
She should have protected herself better.

941
01:01:36,320 --> 01:01:41,560
那埃利斯老师和黄蜂呢
And Mrs. Ellis and the wasps?

942
01:01:41,660 --> 01:01:45,860
还有今晚 你对克洛伊做了什么
And tonight, what did you do to Chloe?

943
01:01:47,200 --> 01:01:49,470
艾玛
Emma!

944
01:01:49,540 --> 01:01:51,030
警长迟早会发现这事实真相的
The sheriff will get to the bottom of this eventually

945
01:01:51,140 --> 01:01:52,240
所以别再该死地骗我了
so don't give me the bullshit story.

946
01:01:52,340 --> 01:01:53,500
你说了"该死"
You said "bullshit".

947
01:01:53,570 --> 01:01:57,170
艾玛 你知道你会怎么样吗
Emma, do you know what could happen to you?!

948
01:01:57,280 --> 01:02:00,940
知道吗
Do you?!

949
01:02:01,010 --> 01:02:04,380
我们会怎么样
What could happen to us?

950
01:02:04,480 --> 01:02:06,780
知道 爸爸
Yes, daddy.

951
01:02:06,890 --> 01:02:08,550
他们会抓走我然后把我送上
They're gonna take me and they're gonna put me

952
01:02:08,620 --> 01:02:12,520
小椅子 粉色小电椅
in the little chair, the little pink electric chair.

953
01:02:12,620 --> 01:02:15,390
我真的不想去
I really don't wanna go there.

954
01:02:15,460 --> 01:02:17,330
我不想尿到自己身上
I don't wanna pee myself.

955
01:02:17,430 --> 01:02:19,400
艾玛 你在说什么
Emma, what're you talking about?

956
01:02:19,470 --> 01:02:20,500
克洛伊说我伤害麦洛
Chloe said she knew about

957
01:02:20,500 --> 01:02:25,500
这事总有一天会被大家知道
Milo and one day everyone would.

958
01:02:25,570 --> 01:02:26,870
她说他们会把我
She said that they were gonna take me

959
01:02:26,940 --> 01:02:31,040
送上专门放小孩子的电椅
to this little electric chair that they put kids in.

960
01:02:31,110 --> 01:02:33,610
还告诉我说她会做我的继母
She told me she was gonna be my stepmother.

961
01:02:33,710 --> 01:02:34,580
艾玛 冷静
Emma, calm down.

962
01:02:34,650 --> 01:02:36,910
我不想要继母
I don't want a stepmother!

963
01:02:37,020 --> 01:02:38,620
绝不
Ever!

964
01:02:41,950 --> 01:02:45,220
她从你房间偷药片
She stole pills from your room.

965
01:02:45,320 --> 01:02:48,190
我看见了
I watched.

966
01:02:48,290 --> 01:02:51,090
她欺骗你
She fooled you.

967
01:02:51,160 --> 01:02:53,860
你不会做任何事
You weren't gonna do anything about it.

968
01:02:53,970 --> 01:02:59,040
什么都不会
Not one thing!

969
01:02:59,140 --> 01:03:02,370
所以你杀了她
So you did.

970
01:03:02,470 --> 01:03:06,740
是不是这样
Isn't that right?

971
01:03:06,850 --> 01:03:09,610
也是迫不得已
Someone had to.

972
01:03:16,090 --> 01:03:17,320
我是马奇医生
This is Dr. March.

973
01:03:17,390 --> 01:03:19,120
之后两周我可能会不在
I'm out of the office for the next two weeks.

974
01:03:19,190 --> 01:03:21,860
如有急事 可以打报警电话
If this is an emergency please call 911

975
